Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: webmonitor
Version: 0.3
Summary: Monitors a website by retrieving it periodically, complains if its down.
Home-page: http://github.com/mbr/webmonitor
Author: Marc Brinkmann
Author-email: git@marcbrinkmann.de
License: MIT
Description: Simple Website monitoring
        =========================
        
        Step 1
        ------
        
        Install::
        
            pip install webmonitor
        
        
        Step 2
        ------
        
        Monitor!::
        
            webmonitor http://google.de
        
        
        That's it
        ---------
        
        Especially good for pinging *cough* Heroku dynos.
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
